# HRIS Project Core Rules

- Preserve existing behavior unless user asks for refactor.
- Keep changes focused; avoid broad rewrites.
- Align frontend behavior with backend API contracts.
- After substantial edits, run `npm run lint` and `npm run build`.
- If schema or seed changes, run `npm run db:setup`.
- Never commit or expose credentials from `.env`.
